desc: My Posing Coach content is relevant and up to date, totally independent of any federation. Professional posing coaching, choreography and personal training. Amy is an accomplished teacher and choreographer for male and female competitors, from first timers to seasoned professional athletes.

layout.text: Get 1 on 1 personal coaching from the first ever female to win professional status in the Women’s Physique Division for the IFBB Pro League Australia. Amy has trained several champions in various divisions and has a reputation for achieving remarkable transformations for her clients.
